PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Industry, Science and Technology of Allister Angus MacKenzie, of Marion Bridge, Nova Scotia, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Cape Breton Development Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of J. Clair Callaghan, whose term has expired.
